## Topic Haritası

| Topic | Publisher | Subscriber(s) | Mesaj Tipi |
|-------|----------|---------------|------------|
| `/antigravity/telemetry_status` | telemetry_monitor | safety_watchdog, mission_commander | `TelemetryStatus` |
| `/antigravity/target_info` | vision_processor | mission_commander | `TargetInfo` |
| `/antigravity/safety_override` | safety_watchdog | trajectory_generator | `SafetyOverride` |
| `/antigravity/mission_command` | mission_commander | trajectory_generator | `MissionCommand` |
| `/uav1/mock_dynamic_wp` | Terminal (pub) | mission_commander | `geometry_msgs/Point` |
| `/uav1/mock_nfz` | Terminal (pub) | mission_commander | `geometry_msgs/Point` |
| `/uav1/mock_target` | Terminal (pub) | vision_processor | `geometry_msgs/Point` |

## Verification Plan

### Build Kontrolü
```bash
cd ~/otopilot_ws
colcon build --packages-select iha_messages iha_otopilot
source install/setup.bash
ros2 launch iha_otopilot antigravity_bringup.launch.py
```

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Gerçek uçuş testi PX4 SITL + Gazebo + MAVROS ortamında yapılmalıdır.
